title: US Open squash: Dipika Pallikal progresses, Joshna Chinappa loses - newsR
text:
*New Delhi*: India's Dipika Pallikal returned to top form after two forgettable tournaments as she notched up one of the best wins of her career, outplaying fourth seeded Alison Waters of England in five games to enter the quarterfinals of the US Open squash in Philadelphia.
The Indian posted a 9-11 11-5 3-11 11-1 11-6 victory ... Â»
